data.description: Unique opportunity in Vinton.  Zoned RB- Residential Business. Would make a great home or office.  Quality-built one-owner vintage 1959 colonial on almost one acre. Beautiful hardwood flooring throughout. Great floor plan with 4 bedrooms. Walk to Lake Drive plaza Kroger, Lancerlot, Rosie's Gaming Emporium, etc.  Take a look!! Great quality in this home.Valley Metro just a short walk away!
